BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 164.88 740 Td (COGNITIVE DISTORTIONS IN SOCIAL SITUATIONS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 700 Td (MIND READING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 682 Td (Assuming you know what others think about you.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 666 Td (Example: 'They think I'm boring' \(without evidence\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 638 Td (FORTUNE TELLING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 620 Td (Predicting negative outcomes before they happen.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 604 Td (Example: 'I'll definitely embarrass myself at the party') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 576 Td (SPOTLIGHT EFFECT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 558 Td (Believing everyone notices your anxiety.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 542 Td (Example: 'Everyone can see I'm blushing/sweating') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 514 Td (CATASTROPHIZING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 496 Td (Blowing consequences out of proportion.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 480 Td (Example: 'If I say something wrong, everyone will hate me') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 452 Td (DISQUALIFYING THE POSITIVE:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 434 Td (Dismissing positive social experiences.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 418 Td (Example: 'They were just being polite, they don't really like me') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 390 Td (EMOTIONAL REASONING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 372 Td (Feeling anxious = something IS wrong.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 356 Td (Example: 'I feel awkward so I must BE awkward') Tj ET

endstream
endobj
