BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 186.96 740 Td (POST-EVENT PROCESSING REDUCTION) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 700 Td (Post-event processing \(PEP\) = replaying social situations in your mind,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 683 Td (focusing on everything you did 'wrong.' This MAINTAINS social anxiety.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 650 Td (When you catch yourself ruminating:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 625 Td (1. NOTICE: 'I'm doing post-event processing right now.') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 603 Td (2. REDIRECT: Shift attention to present moment \(5 senses\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 581 Td (3. REMIND: 'My anxious brain exaggerates. The reality was probably fine.') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 559 Td (4. STOP: Set a rule - no analyzing social events after they're over.) Tj ET
