BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 198.48000000000002 740 Td (ATTENTION TRAINING EXERCISES) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 700 Td (Social anxiety makes you SELF-FOCUSED. The cure: shift to EXTERNAL focus.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 670 Td (Exercise 1: The Observer) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 650 Td (In a social situation, focus entirely on the OTHER person. Notice their eye) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 635 Td (color, what they're wearing, their tone. You can't be self-conscious if all) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 620 Td (your attention is on them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 595 Td (Exercise 2: The Reporter) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 575 Td (Pretend you're a journalist. Your job is to find out 3 interesting things) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 560 Td (about each person you talk to. Ask questions. Listen to answers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 535 Td (Exercise 3: The Noticer) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 515 Td (In a group, notice 5 things about the environment. What's on the walls?) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 500 Td (What music is playing? What are people eating? Get OUT of your head.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 475 Td (Exercise 4: The Helper) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 455 Td (Focus on making the OTHER person comfortable. This shifts your brain from) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 440 Td ('Am I okay?' to 'Are THEY okay?' - and reduces self-focus.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
